data.description: Welcome to your new home in the heart of historic York! This charming ranch-style house boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a layout that just keeps on giving. With brand new carpeting, fresh paint, and a spacious primary bedroom with an en-suite bathroom, this property offers comfort and convenience for you and your family. Additionally, the unique feature of a separate entrance to the 3rd bedroom makes it perfect for in-laws or teenagers seeking their own space. Located just a short distance from all that historic York has to offer, this home is ready to welcome you with open arms.
